INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('86', '1', '2015-12-20 07:51:53', '2015-12-20 07:51:53', 'In 2012, three friends working together at a dispensary saw a need for lab tested, accurately dosed, safely manufactured and delicious edibles. They created a vision of what a conscious cannabis company would look like, found a world class chocolatier, studied safe extraction methods for cannabis and began to create a variety of products for the patients at their dispensary. They entered the Santa Cruz Cannabis Cup later that year and took first place for their indica dark chocolate bar. It was then that they knew they had something special, and set out to create a company with the safest and most delicious products possible. Just three years later, Freedom Enterprises has grown to include four brands and over 50 employees, including a full-time scientist. Hashman Infused focuses on edible cannabis products, providing patients with a healthy and discreet way to take their medicine.[/text_output][/container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][container][text_output]\n\nOUR BELIEFS\n\n[/text_output][line][text_output]\n\nWe believe in conscious capitalism, doing good and having fun!!\nWe believe in paying living wages, providing benefits and opportunities to our employees.\nWe believe in producing only high quality, healthy products that provide healing and happiness.\nWe believe in sourcing local, fair trade and organic products whenever possible.\nWe believe in sourcing sustainable, recyclable, compostable materials and packaging.\nWe believe in using science, testing and innovation to provide safe, effective and consistent products.', 'ABOUT US', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '15-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-12-20 07:51:53', '2015-12-20 07:51:53', '', '15', 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress_hashman/2015/12/20/15-autosave-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
