INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('93', '1', '2015-12-20 08:02:11', '2015-12-20 08:02:11', 'Hey we would like to say thank you for the tour ! Every one there works hard and shows passion in there work ! Like I said you can taste it in the chocolate. We had an awesome time and enjoyed the process from start to finish. Thank you for everything you have given us ! Your facility and staff go the extra mile and as patients we appreciate it .With the care you all put into your work I bet you can make an amazing cake pop.Maybe if it\'s possible create a lotion or cream to rub on muscles for aches and pain.\r\n\r\nThank you for your great hospitality and the tour . We really learned a lot from this experience.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n\r\nNicolas Jimenez\r\nKaeleigh Lara\r\n\r\n\r\nTo whomever this may concern,\r\n\r\nHello, I\'m Tyler Muñoz and September of 2014 at only 20 years old I was diagnosed with stage IV glioblastoma brain cancer. The first couple weeks were very challenging for me to fight this battle. I noticed myself going down hill pretty fast. While in the hospital my girlfriend and family members were looking into how cannabis can help fight cancer and attack brain tumors. They checked out many different clubs and after trying out so many different types of cannabis oil, we finally got recommended to, \"Jake, from Hashman Infused\". Weeks after taking their products I noticed my life going more up hill. I have used products such as the tincture drops, chocolate bars and cookies. The main products that I have been taking since October of 2014 are the cannabis capsules. Not only have Hashman products helped me with my pain, nausea and vomiting, but I strongly believe that because of these amazing products, my tumors have once shrunk by 20% this past January. I still continue to use Hashman products for all the reasons above, and also to boost my energy levels with the AM capsules and relax me with the PM capsules. I have had a very hard time eating, due to no appetite, but after doubling my cannabis dosage, I do find myself eating a tad bit better.\r\n\r\nI would like to thank Jake and his team from Hashman infused for their wonderful life changing products, and for always believing in me.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n\r\nTyler Muñoz', 'TESTIMONIALS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '35-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-20 08:02:11', '2015-12-20 08:02:11', '', '35', 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress_hashman/2015/12/20/35-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
