n\r\n- Partner with the sales and marketing teams to gather detailed information to support our team\r\n\r\nand brand.\r\n\r\n-Responsible for planning and budgetary control of all social media marketing.\r\n\r\n-Graph design and content building for digital and print material. Be able to use Photoshop and\r\n\r\nother editing tools.\r\n\r\n-Other duties as assigned.\r\n\r\nJob Qualifications\r\n- Strategic thinker with the ability to understand how digital marketing and social\r\n\r\nmedia strategies can best achieve overall sales and marketing objectives\r\n\r\n-Must be already plugged into social media landscape, aware of trends and be able\r\n\r\nto continually monitor for trends and emerging platforms and react quickly\r\n\r\n-Ability to work independently, take initiative, solve practical problems and organize\r\n\r\nworkload for effective implementation under minimal supervision.\r\n\r\n-Editorial judgment with exceptional writing skills, particularly for the web,\r\n\r\nutilizing best practices of search optimization\r\nExcellent\r\n-Review new social media tools, trends and applications and understand implications\r\n\r\nof changes in social media trends\r\n\r\n-Experience with online social media metrics tools\r\n\r\n-Proficient in MS Office components, Photoshop and any other needed tools.\r\n\r\n- Photography and video is not a must but very desirable for this position\r\n\r\n-Well organized and able to manage multiple projects simultaneously required\r\n\r\n-Ability to organize workload for effective, timely implementation\r\n\r\n-Understands sense of urgency and attention to detail\r\n\r\n-Enthusiastic and proactive orientation with a \"can-do\" attitude\r\n\r\n-Awareness of social media influencers, sites, apps, and relevant content in\r\n\r\nconnection with the beauty, personal care, health and/or wellness industry\r\n\r\npreferred\r\n\r\n-Grow our brand awareness and maintain contact with customers through our Social\r\n\r\nmedia platforms.\r\n\r\nExperience\r\n-3-5 years of experience utilizing and managing successful social media and\r\n\r\ncommunications campaigns and strategies\r\n\r\n-Demonstrated professional experience using Twitter, LinkedIn, Facebook, Google,\r\n\r\nYouTube, blogs, etc. to advance business development and marketing media\r\n\r\nobjectives\r\n\r\n-Excel in graphic design and content creation\r\n\r\nTo Apply Email -  info@freedom-enterprises.biz\r\n\r\nWith a cover letter and resume, links to social media accounts you have worked on and an example of your graphic design work. We are looking to hire ASAP !', 'CAREER OPPORTUNITIES', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-12-20 08:04:22', '2015-12-20 08:04:22', '', '41', 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress_hashman/2015/12/20/41-autosave-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
