INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('292', '2', '2016-01-12 06:21:33', '2016-01-12 06:21:33', '[cs_section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 45px 0px; \"][cs_row style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; \" inner_container=\"true\"][cs_column style=\"padding: 0px; \" fade_animation=\"in\" fade_animation_offset=\"45px\" fade_duration=\"750\" type=\"1/2\"][cs_text]<h4>Testing &amp; Test Results: Our Philosophy</h4>\nHashman Infused is committed to producing high-quality, safe and appropriately dosed medical cannabis products.\n\nWe demonstrate our commitment by the fact that we use high-quality California-grown raw material and we work with a staff scientist as well as a world-class chocolatier to produce our edibles.\n\nEqually importantly, we also subject our products to rigorous testing throughout our entire manufacturing process. The purpose of testing is to ensure that we consistently meet and exceed the highest standards in the medical cannabis industry.\n\nSince we hold ourselves to such a high standard, we only work with the best when testing our medicine. SC Labs is the recognized leader in quality assurance and safety testing Medical Cannabis.\n\nWe have SC Labs test our raw materials and also the finished products so that you can be assured that our product quality and safety is independently verified by a third party. To ensure that we pass those every time, we also have our own internal testing program of the materials, the product as it goes through the manufacturing process, and the final results. We’re proud to deliver best medicine that is high-quality, accurately dosed, and safe!\n\nFeel free to review the sample test results for our Cherry Bomb Chocolate bar![/cs_text][/cs_column][cs_column style=\"padding: 0px; \" fade_animation=\"in\" fade_animation_offset=\"45px\" fade_duration=\"750\" type=\"1/2\"][x_image type=\"none\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wordpress_hashman/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Cherry-Bomb-4292015-1.png\" alt=\"\" link=\"false\" href=\"#\" title=\"\" target=\"\" info=\"none\" info_place=\"top\" info_trigger=\"hover\" info_content=\"\"][/cs_column][/cs_row][/cs_section]', 'TEST RESULTS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '31-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-12 06:21:33', '2016-01-12 06:21:33', '', '31', 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress_hashman/2016/01/12/31-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('293', '2', '2016-01-12 06:22:36', '2016-01-12 06:22:36', '[cs_section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 45px 0px; \"][cs_row style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; \" inner_container=\"true\"][cs_column style=\"padding: 0px; \" fade_animation=\"in\" fade_animation_offset=\"45px\" fade_duration=\"750\" type=\"2/3\"][cs_text]<strong>Our Story</strong>\n\nIn 2012, three friends working together at a dispensary saw a need for delicious high-quality edibles that were lab tested, accurately dosed, and safely manufactured.\n\nThey had a vision of what a conscious cannabis company could look like. To get started, they sought out organic, high quality raw material, they studied safe extraction methods for cannabis and they teamed up with world-class chocolatier a to create a variety of products for the patients at their dispensary.\n\nLater that year, they entered the Santa Cruz Cannabis Cup and took first place for their indica dark chocolate bar. That’s when they knew had something special! The trio set set out to create a company with the safest and most delicious products possible.\n\nJust three years later, Freedom Enterprises has grown to include four brands and over 50 employees, including a full-time scientist. Hashman Infused focuses on high-quality edible cannabis products, providing patients with a safe, healthy, discrete and accurately dosed way to take their medicine.[/cs_text][/cs_column][cs_column style=\"padding: 0px; \" fade_animation=\"in\" fade_animation_offset=\"45px\" fade_duration=\"750\" type=\"1/3\"][cs_text]<strong>Our Beliefs</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>We believe in conscious capitalism, doing good and having fun!!</li>\n	<li>We believe in producing only high quality, healthy products that provide healing and happiness</li>\n	<li>We believe in sourcing local, fair trade and organic products whenever possible</li>\n	<li>We believe in sourcing sustainable, recyclable, compostable materials and packaging</li>\n	<li>We believe in using science, testing and innovation to provide safe, effective and consistent products</li>\n</ul>[/cs_text][/cs_column][/cs_row][/cs_section]', 'ABOUT US', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-12 06:22:36', '2016-01-12 06:22:36', '', '15', 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress_hashman/2016/01/12/15-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('294', '2', '2016-01-12 06:24:57', '2016-01-12 06:24:57', '[cs_section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 45px 0px; \"][cs_row style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; \" inner_container=\"true\"][cs_column style=\"padding: 0px; \" fade_animation=\"in\" fade_animation_offset=\"45px\" fade_duration=\"750\" type=\"2/3\"][cs_text]<h3>Our Story</h3>\nIn 2012, three friends working together at a dispensary saw a need for delicious high-quality edibles that were lab tested, accurately dosed, and safely manufactured.\n\nThey had a vision of what a conscious cannabis company could look like. To get started, they sought out organic, high quality raw material, they studied safe extraction methods for cannabis and they teamed up with world-class chocolatier a to create a variety of products for the patients at their dispensary.\n\nLater that year, they entered the Santa Cruz Cannabis Cup and took first place for their indica dark chocolate bar. That’s when they knew had something special! The trio set set out to create a company with the safest and most delicious products possible.\n\nJust three years later, Freedom Enterprises has grown to include four brands and over 50 employees, including a full-time scientist. Hashman Infused focuses on high-quality edible cannabis products, providing patients with a safe, healthy, discrete and accurately dosed way to take their medicine.[/cs_text][/cs_column][cs_column style=\"padding: 0px; \" fade_animation=\"in\" fade_animation_offset=\"45px\" fade_duration=\"750\" type=\"1/3\"][cs_text]<h3><strong>Our Beliefs</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li>We believe in conscious capitalism, doing good and having fun!!</li>\n	<li>We believe in producing only high quality, healthy products that provide healing and happiness</li>\n	<li>We believe in sourcing local, fair trade and organic products whenever possible</li>\n	<li>We believe in sourcing sustainable, recyclable, compostable materials and packaging</li>\n	<li>We believe in using science, testing and innovation to provide safe, effective and consistent products</li>\n</ul>[/cs_text][/cs_column][/cs_row][/cs_section][cs_section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 45px 0px; \"][cs_row style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; \" inner_container=\"true\"][cs_column style=\"padding: 0px; \" fade_animation=\"in\" fade_animation_offset=\"45px\" fade_duration=\"750\" type=\"1/1\"][x_image type=\"circle\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wordpress_hashman/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/PHOTO_20151226_165544.jpg\" alt=\"\" link=\"false\" href=\"#\" title=\"\" target=\"\" info=\"none\" info_place=\"top\" info_trigger=\"hover\" info_content=\"\"][/cs_column][/cs_row][/cs_section]', 'ABOUT US', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-12 06:24:57', '2016-01-12 06:24:57', '', '15', 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress_hashman/2016/01/12/15-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('295', '2', '2016-01-12 06:34:54', '2016-01-12 06:34:54', '[cs_section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 45px 0px; \"][cs_row style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; \" inner_container=\"true\"][cs_column style=\"padding: 0px; \" fade_animation=\"in\" fade_animation_offset=\"45px\" fade_duration=\"750\" type=\"1/1\"][x_feature_list][x_feature_box title=\"What are CBD, Indica and Sativa? What&#039;s the difference?\" title_color=\"\" text_color=\"\" graphic=\"icon\" graphic_size=\"60px\" graphic_shape=\"hexagon\" graphic_color=\"#ffffff\" graphic_bg_color=\"#2b7f27\" align_h=\"left\" align_v=\"top\" side_graphic_spacing=\"20px\" max_width=\"none\" child=\"true\" connector_width=\"1px\" connector_style=\"dashed\" connector_color=\"#272727\" graphic_icon=\"gg\"]Cannabidiol (or CBD) is one of many active compounds in cannabis; it is an cannabinoid, like THC. Unlike THC, CBD is non-psychoactive (it doesn’t give the user a high) and is therefore popular among patients that do not want THC in their medicine.\n\nIndica and sativa are two different species of cannabis that look different and have different effects when consumed. They each can contain different kinds of cannabinoids, including THC and CBC. \n\nPatients can tailor their product choices depending on what therapeutic properties they seek. Many of our products are available in Indica, Sativa, and CBD formulas. \n\nHere’s a general guide to the effects you can expect:\n\nIndica formulations give patients a relaxing, sedating experience with full-body effects. It is generally recommended to take Indica medicine in the evening.\n\nSativa formulations provide cerebral, uplifting effects. Sativa medicine is usually taken earlier in the day.\n\nFormulations that are high in CBD can offer a wide variety of health benefits. High-CBD medicine has been known to combat nausea, seizures, inflammation, anxiety and even cancer cells, all without the psychoactive effects of THC.[/x_feature_box][x_featu